# Minime Alpine world (H700) — board-specific package set.
#
# H700 ships Mali Bifrost G31 (Allwinner).  The Mali driver is the
# proprietary libmali / mali_kbase pair; both are intentionally absent
# from this list (the build also has `mali_kbase` removed from the kernel
# for Alpine).  V1 accepts the G31's lower GLES throughput under Panfrost
# through the GPU's display path; the UI is still accelerated through
# DRM/GBM/KMS, just without the Mali-specific userspace.
#
# Board-specific deltas:
#   - H700 DTBs use the Sun50i H616/H700 platform with AXP223 PMIC; the
#     bus-only AXP223 regulator device tree is sufficient and no extra
#     userspace packages are needed beyond world-common.

# Inherit world-common behavior is provided by build.sh, which concatenates
# world-common and world-<board> at install time.  This file currently
# contributes no extra packages, but is preserved so the board delta
# remains explicit and version-controllable.
